Description:
    Wires the app for collaborative Lexxy editing: a DocumentChannel that
    joins clients by signed GlobalID and materializes edits back into
    Action Text, plus the storage migration (yrby's Y::Document +
    Y::DocumentUpdate tables) and the lexxy-realtime JavaScript import.

Example:
    bin/rails generate lexxy_realtime:install

    This will create:
        app/channels/document_channel.rb
        app/channels/application_cable/{connection,channel}.rb  (if missing)
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXX_create_yrby_tables.rb
    and append `import "lexxy-realtime"` to app/javascript/application.js.
    The models ship in the gems (Y::Document, Y::DocumentUpdate).
